</li><li style=3D"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontServi=
ce, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
<div style=3D"margin: 1em 0px;" role=3D"presentation" class=3D"elementToPro=
of"><b>Prime v3 (UE / IDP):</b>&nbsp;Coverage expanded rapidly (<b>~255+ te=
st cases</b>) driven by NYD requirements, IDP changes (e.g., international =
phone numbers), and proactive gap closure.</div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontServi=
ce, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
<div style=3D"margin: 1em 0px;" role=3D"presentation" class=3D"elementToPro=
of"><b>API Automation:</b>&nbsp;Authentication slice implemented, validated=
 in Stage1/QC4, and ready for pipeline onboarding.</div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontServi=
ce, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
<div style=3D"margin: 1em 0px;" role=3D"presentation" class=3D"elementToPro=
of"><b>Performance Testing:</b>&nbsp;Ownership transitioned to QA; auth flo=
ws understood; baseline stabilization in progress.</div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontServi=
ce, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
<div style=3D"margin: 1em 0px;" role=3D"presentation" class=3D"elementToPro=
